# Home

The Home page is the default landing page for all authenticated users (route `/`).
It is planned to display a personalised overview dashboard, with the content varying
by the viewer's role and relationships within the system.

---

## Planned Content

### All users

- Summary of their own account (name, role, status, last login).

### Employees

- Their assigned company and position.
- Manager list — names and contact details of direct managers.
- Managee list — names and contact details of direct reports.
- Ability to navigate the management chain (click a manager/managee to view their
  own manager and managee relationships in turn).

### Owners

- Overview of companies they own (status, employee count).
- Quick links to the Companies and Employees admin pages.

### Admins

- High-level system summary: total users, companies, employees.
- Quick links to all admin sections (Owners, Users, Companies, Employees).

---

## Route

`/` — index route inside the authenticated `Layout`. Accessible to any logged-in user.
No additional role guard is applied.
